# gitdeck

GitHub repo vigilance. Watches owned, competitor, provider, consumer, and benchmark repos; routes findings to crunchdeck.

## Usage
- Configure repos to watch: edit `REPOS.md`, or `flowdeck blueprint use gitdeck-add-repo`
- Run all watchers: play `repos/TODO.md`
- Findings land under `repos/<slug>/findings/` — activate `send-to-crunchdeck`, `create-card`, or `discard` on each

## Structure
- `REPOS.md` — the watch list (edit to add/remove repos)
- `repos/<slug>/REPO.md` + `TODO.md` — one per watched repo, with a run log
- `ACTIONS.md` — reference for finding-card actions
